@startuml DLQ_Retry_Flow
title Dead Letter Queue - Retry Flow

participant "Producer" as producer
queue "Основной топик (booking.trip.lifecycle.v1)" as main_topic
participant "Consumer" as consumer
queue "Retry Topic (internal)" as retry_topic
queue "DLQ Topic (booking.trip.lifecycle.v1.dlq)" as dlq
participant "Alertmanager -> PagerDuty/Slack" as alerting
participant "On-call инженер" as oncall

== Happy Path ==
producer -> main_topic: Publish event
main_topic -> consumer: Poll
consumer -> consumer: Обработка OK
consumer -> main_topic: ACK

== Retry Flow ==
producer -> main_topic: Publish event
main_topic -> consumer: Poll
consumer -> consumer: Ошибка обработки

consumer -> retry_topic: Попытка 1 (delay: 1 сек)
note right: Транзиентная ошибка (таймаут сети)
retry_topic -> consumer: Retry
consumer -> consumer: Ошибка

consumer -> retry_topic: Попытка 2 (delay: 10 сек)
note right: Кратковременная недоступность
retry_topic -> consumer: Retry
consumer -> consumer: Ошибка

consumer -> retry_topic: Попытка 3 (delay: 60 сек)
note right: Продолжительная недоступность
retry_topic -> consumer: Retry
consumer -> consumer: Ошибка

== DLQ ==
consumer -> dlq: Все 3 попытки исчерпаны -> отправка в DLQ
note right of dlq
  DLQ-событие содержит:
  - original_event
  - error (message + stack)
  - retry_count: 3
  - timestamps
end note

dlq -> alerting: dlq_messages_total > 0
alerting -> oncall: Алерт (P1 для payment.*.dlq P3 для notification.*.dlq)

oncall -> dlq: Анализ причины
oncall -> main_topic: Ручной reprocess (после исправления)

@enduml
